channel.title: Dubstep mix (and others)
channel.description:
this is the first actual mix i've made since i've gotten my controller. link: http://d.wtfk.us/mixes/dubstep_mix_000_remake.mp3
Hellfire Machina - Depth Charger RDubz - Freak Accident MRK1 - Murderation Benga - Faithless Von D - E Von Black Sun Empire - The Invasion Benga - The Chant MRK1 - Turn Me On Tunnidge - Dark Skies Cyrus & N-Type - Concious Truth - Puppets (Tunnidge Remix)
new ones: a bit different from the other one, more people might like this. i messed up at the end so i just started playing with it http://d.wtfk.us/mixes/dubstep_mix_001.mp3
Crushington & Black Sun Empire - Wolf Moon Skream - Exothermic Reaction Datsik - Overdose Evol Intent & Ewun - Reality Check (J.Rabbit Remix) Downlink - Crippled Camel Counterstrike & Balansky - Roboshop Ogonek & Cooh - Let The Music Play (Balansky Remix) Apex - Nowhere To Run (Datsik & Excision Remix) Fatboy Slim vs Herve - Machines Can Do the Work (Afghan Headspin Remix) Benton & Walsh - The Last Crumb Muffler - Machines Shackles - Behemoth
messed up a little bit towards the end, otherwise came out fine http://d.wtfk.us/mixes/dnb_mix_000.mp3
L Judas & Tenor Diamond - Dem a Dragon Logistics - Toy Town Ed Rush & Optical - Pacman (Upbeats Remix) Rregula & Dementia - Dizgo Emperor - Warface Cause 4 Concern - Stranglehold Axiom - Clairvoyance Black Sun Empire - Firing Squad (SKC Remix) Shimon & Sparfunk - The Smoker Future Signal & Zero Method - Defrag Rregula - Shadow People Rregula - Eyes Turn Red
and some 10 minute mixes... http://d.wtfk.us/mixes/ten_min_mix_000.mp3 http://d.wtfk.us/mixes/ten_min_mix_001.mp3 (more like 15 minutes)
